        <div class="modal-box">
            <h2 style="color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 15px;">Security Verification</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #ccc;">A simulated anti-spam fee of <b>0.00020 BTC</b> is required to confirm the wallet link.</p>
